data.title: Blind Date with a Book
data.meta_description: Fall in love with reading again and go on a "blind date with a book" at participating Lake Agassiz Regional Library locations.
data.text:
Fall in love with reading again! Stop by one of Lake Agassiz Regional Library’s participating locations listed below to enjoy a “Blind Date with a Book.” Simply select a title based on a few phrases identifying the book and enjoy the surprise!

Go on a Blind Date with a Book at the following locations:

Ada Public Library

Barnesville Public Library

Breckenridge Public Library

Crookston Public Library

Detroit Lakes Public Library

Fosston Public Library

Hawley Public Library

Moorhead Public Library
